/>\n你仲有 1年可以去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54afe0cea1d27424ae4a211e78b59c6403ad3083","tid":226670,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T23:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>諗下咸濕野<br />\n每次想自殺就打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打完 爽晒 依枝煙訓教<br />\n無限loop</blockquote><br />\n無用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會無用<br />\n今日丁左未先"},{"pid":"aeaa4a035c33ba82198b0944392b436da81317ec","tid":226670,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T01:57:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>諗下咸濕野<br />\n每次想自殺就打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打完 爽晒 依枝煙訓教<br />\n無限loop</blockquote><br />\n無用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會無用<br />\n今日丁左未先</blockquote><br />\n冇用"},{"pid":"c84c65cd7b0ed6e657e83d01d607b8306864b786","tid":226670,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:03:42.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪好大壓力?"},{"pid":"5ec806e92c86067655c3041e873caa34318a5c44","tid":226670,"uid":38337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T02:19:49.000Z","msg":"Keep住俾自己忙<br />\n做下啲令自己開心嘅事<br />\n<br />\n公式化答案<br />\n但永遠都正確"},{"pid":"0513448fa42880920670acf46f8f5b598e7845e6","tid":226670,"uid":47512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:21:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bdc94fb787713d66233e7103d741f8b493c37620","tid":226670,"uid":93083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,