ote>如果兩老唔係到 可能我早就走左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsame here"},{"pid":"ad527134958a4784a5c83cda8e0dd5ef49ce6fe1","tid":226670,"uid":72330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T16:45:08.000Z","msg":"我有時都會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又怕 唔敢死<br />\n1開始ex都會驚我有事然後擔心我<br />\n但我每次都無事然後佢就無理我了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd51d7ec832e0c7f56d1d83e84c7c6264baa02e5","tid":226670,"uid":76479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:01:34.000Z","msg":"今日唔知聽日事，今日死左<br />\n聽日會發生咩你唔會知<br />\n聽日會中六合彩你唔會知<br />\n聽日你成功左你唔會知<br />\n聽日你老母煮咩飯你唔會知<br />\n<br />\n自殺唔係解決一切既方法，只係逃避一切，包括你聽日，你未來會發生既事<br />\n<br />\n你可以話你生活係壓力之下，但你永遠都唔會係最慘，因為你仲可以決定自己既生死<br />\n你要記得有D人就連自己既生死都不能控制"},{"pid":"ee93faf55ed658de3515b4e49d662dbd52e742a3","tid":226670,"uid":68941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:09:35.000Z","msg":"好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e833c234f273cf150e93c760374d23d6d631fc","tid":226670,"uid":14217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:12:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZXsQAXx_ao0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZXsQAXx_ao0&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnhwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=e3bb4e51\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZXsQAXx_ao0</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5716e904e98d1926cae63152a9e4f7b83df68f0","tid":226670,"uid":68941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:15:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZXsQAXx_ao0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZXsQAXx_ao0&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnhwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=e3bb4e51\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZXsQAXx_ao0</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/n